headline.print_headline: Cabin Stowaway Caught After Flying to Los Angeles on Commercial Flight
headline.main: Cabin Stowaway Caught After Flying to Los Angeles on Commercial Flight

lead_paragraph: A ticketless traveler managed to sneak aboard a commercial flight undetected at the San Jose International Airport and fly to Los Angeles in at least the second major security breach involving a stowaway there this year, authorities said on Wednesday.
